# v0.34 onboarding §11 decision #6: dogfood the Coral marketplace on
# this repo itself so contributors who clone + open Claude Code see
# the plugin offered. Everything else under .claude/ (local IDE
# state, scheduled-tasks locks, settings.local.json overrides) stays
# ignored — only this one shared file ships.
!.claude/settings.json
